   function calcCommission(){\n        var first = true;\n        var userPercent = parseFloat($(\"#userPercent\").val());\n        if (isNaN(userPercent)){\n            userPercent = 0;\n        } else {\n            userPercent = userPercent / 100;\n        }\n        $(\"table.producttable\").find(\"tr\").each(function(){\n            if (first){\n                first = false;\n            } else {\n                var tr = $(this);\n                var tdPrice = tr.find(\"td.price:first\");\n                var tdCommission = tr.find(\"td.commission:first\");\n                var tdSysCommission = tr.find(\"td.sysCommission:first\");\n                var ali = tr.find(\"td.ali:first\");\n                var price = parseFloat(tdPrice.attr(\"alt\"));\n                var commission = parseFloat(tdCommission.attr(\"alt\"));\n                var priceCommission = parseFloat(tdPrice.attr(\"comm\"));\n                var specCommission = tdPrice.attr(\"spec\") == 'true';\n                var rec = parseFloat(tdPrice.attr(\"rec\"));\n                var langId = $(\"#sys-lang-input\").val();\n                if (!isNaN(price) && !isNaN(priceCommission)) {\n\n                    var optPrice = price - priceCommission;\n                    var _price = optPrice + optPrice * userPercent;\n                    if (_price < price) {\n                        _price = price;\n                    }\n                    var proc = 0.7;\n                    var _commission = (_price - optPrice) * proc;\n                    var _sysCommission = (_price - optPrice) *0.3;\n                    //alert(optPrice)\n                    if (ali) {\n                        var fullCommission = 280.0 + optPrice * userPercent;\n                        var sysPercent = 0.3;\n                        _sysCommission = fullCommission * sysPercent;\n                        _commission = fullCommission - _sysCommission;\n                        \n                    } else if (langId == 1){\n                        var fullCommission = (_price - optPrice);\n                        var sysPercent = 0.3;\n                        _sysCommission = fullCommission * sysPercent;\n                        var minSysComm = specCommission ? 17.05 : 97.4;\n                        if (_sysCommission < minSysComm/*3*42.0*/) {\n                            _sysCommission = minSysComm/*3*42.0*/;\n                        }\n                        var nds = fullCommission * 18.0/100;\n                        _commission = fullCommission - _sysCommission - nds;\n                    }\n    //                var _price = price + price * userPercent;\n    //                var _commission = commission + (price * userPercent)*0.7;\n                    var priceHtml = Math.round(_price*100)/100;\n                    if (userPercent == 0){\n                        priceHtml += \"<a href='#' class='extCom'> + доп. наценка</a>\";\n                        if (!isNaN(rec)) {\n                            priceHtml += \"<br>(\" + rec + \")\";\n                        }\n                    }\n                    var commissionHtml = Math.round(_commission*100)/100;\n                    if (userPercent == 0){\n                        commissionHtml += \"<a href='#' class='extCom'> + доп. наценка</a>\";\n                    }\n                    var sysCommissionHtml = Math.round(_sysCommission*100)/100;\n                    if (userPercent == 0){\n                        sysCommissionHtml += \"<a href='#' class='extCom'> + доп. наценка</a>\";\n                    }\n                    tdPrice.html(priceHtml);\n                    tdCommission.html(commissionHtml);\n                    tdSysCommission.html(sysCommissionHtml);\n                }\n            }\n        });\n    }\n\n    function calcCommission2(id, percent){\n        var userPercent = parseFloat(percent);\n        if (isNaN(userPercent)){\n            userPercent = 0;\n        } else {\n            userPercent = userPercent / 100;\n        }\n        var tr = $(\"tr[alt=\"+id+\"]:first\");\n        var tdPrice = tr.find(\"td.price:first\");\n        var tdCommission = tr.find(\"td.commission:first\");\n        var tdSysCommission = tr.find(\"td.sysCommission:first\");\n        var price = parseFloat(tdPrice.attr(\"alt\"));\n        var commission = parseFloat(tdCommission.attr(\"alt\"));\n        var priceCommission = parseFloat(tdPrice.attr(\"comm\"));\n        var specCommission = tdPrice.attr(\"spec\") == 'true';\n        var rec = parseFloat(tdPrice.attr(\"rec\"));\n        var langId = $(\"#sys-lang-input\").val();\n        if (!isNaN(price) && !isNaN(priceCommission)){\n            var optPrice = price - priceCommission;\n            var _price = optPrice + optPrice * userPercent;\n            if (_price < price) {\n                _price = price;\n            }\n            var proc = 0.7;\n    //        if (priceCommission > 249){\n    //            proc= 0.52;\n    //        }\n            var _commission = (_price - optPrice) * proc;\n            var _sysCommission = (_price - optPrice) *0.3;\n            if (langId == 1){\n                var fullCommission = (_price - optPrice);\n                var sysPercent = 0.3;\n                _sysCommission = fullCommission * sysPercent;\n                var minSysComm = specCommission ? 17.05 : 97.4;\n                if (_sysCommission < minSysComm/*3*42.0*/) {\n                    _sysCommission = minSysComm/*3*42.0*/;\n                }\n                var nds = fullCommission * 18.0/100;\n                _commission = fullCommission - _sysCommission - nds;\n            }\n    //        var _price = price + price * userPercent;\n    //        var _commission = commission + (price * userPercent)*0.7;\n            var priceHtml = Math.round(_price*100)/100;\n            priceHtml += \"<a href='#' class='extCom' alt='\" + (userPercent*100) + \"'> + доп. наценка\";\n            if (userPercent > 0){\n                priceHtml += \" (\" + (userPercent*100) + \"%)\";\n            }\n            priceHtml += \"</a>\";\n            if (!isNaN(rec)) {\n                priceHtml += \"<br>(\" + rec + \")\";\n            }\n            var commissionHtml = Math.round(_commission*100)/100;\n            commissionHtml += \"<a href='#' class='extCom' alt='\" + (userPercent*100) + \"'> + доп. наценка\";\n            if (userPercent > 0){\n                commissionHtml += \" (\" + (userPercent*100) + \"%)\";\n            }\n            commissionHtml += \"</a>\";\n            var sysCommissionHtml = Math.round(_sysCommission*100)/100;\n            sysCommissionHtml += \"<a href='#' class='extCom' alt='\" + (userPercent*100) + \"'> + доп. наценка\";\n            if (userPercent > 0){\n                sysCommissionHtml += \" (\" + (userPercent*100) + \"%)\";\n            }\n            sysCommissionHtml += \"</a>\";\n            tdPrice.html(priceHtml);\n            tdCommission.html(commissionHtml);\n            tdSysCommission.html(sysCommissionHtml);\n        }\n    }\n\n    function calcCommission3(id, uprice){\n        var userPrice = parseFloat(uprice);\n        if (isNaN(userPrice)){\n _sysCommission = (_price - optPrice) *0.3;\n            if (langId == 1){\n                var fullCommission = (_price - optPrice);\n                var sysPercent = 0.3;\n priceHtml += \" (\" + uprice + \" \" + (langId==6?\"грн\":\"руб\") + \")\";\n            }\n            priceHtml += \"</a>\";\n            if (!isNaN(rec)) {\n                priceHtml += \"<br>(\" + наценка\";\n            if (uprice > 0){\n                commissionHtml += \" (\" + uprice + \" \" + (langId==6?\"грн\":\"руб\") + \")\";\n            }\n            commissionHtml += \"</a>\";\n
